{{Mission Description|type=continuance|location=Scalegorge Waterscape|The tide of Scalegorge Waterscape flows ceaselessly, just like the aspiration of the Vidyadhara Preceptors. The arrival of Dan Heng and Lingsha will be the key to deciding the direction of this flow.}}
